    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a roguelike adventure with an electrifying arcade twist. <i>Squad Arcade</i> blends strategic deckbuilding, card-based combat, and retro-futuristic flair into a dynamic experience where every run is unique and every decision matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/3b2a0656521bd7e8d67b94b1081a28ff.avif?t=1770324837\" width=1000 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a post-human future, synthetic animatronic beings stumble upon humanity’s most thrilling legacy: a card game filled with mythical creatures, historical icons, and legendary heroes. Thus begins <i>Squad Arcade</i>—a place where synthetics rediscover the joy of play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/4f477f7f9f88cf999a8efab8ae1fffff.avif?t=1770324837\" width=1000 height=84 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike progression: Face ever-changing challenges with tactical decisions that shape each run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep deckbuilding: Discover over 200 unique cards and create powerful combos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card-based combat: Select up to five cards per turn to form your Squad and battle enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Poker-style plays: Create hands like pairs, triples, straights, and flushes to boost character stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonuses and multipliers: Synergistic plays grant stat boosts and multipliers that turn the tide of battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/5c5f2b6692996075c8d6ae85e5715d51.avif?t=1770324837\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/9799bf0989e3716575178be53cc9335f.avif?t=1770324837\" width=1000 height=84 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple plays in a single hand: Combine elements, fame, and rank to trigger layered synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tactical positioning: Card placement determines which ally fights which enemy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable arcade machines: Over 1,000 gameplay-impacting combinations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visual identity: A bold mix of neon, comic book style, and 80s retro-futurism.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable Comic: The run’s map is generated as you choose which comic page to read each time.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/7f237436c4d83c451f37127aa11b7730.avif?t=1770324837\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/15fc01e24c9f72ff52fec7a3f0182648.avif?t=1770324837\" width=1000 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the Synth Animatronics, each with distinct mechanics:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >L1-Z4RD – Warlord</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ARO-W4NA – Guardian</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PO-0 – Mastermind</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OP-055-UM – Trickster</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/dbb9c267a09e3a2f2a7bd48a5a1ea8ca.poster.avif?t=1770324837\" width=832 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/dbb9c267a09e3a2f2a7bd48a5a1ea8ca.webm?t=1770324837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/dbb9c267a09e3a2f2a7bd48a5a1ea8ca.mp4?t=1770324837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/ae2e0008a7b62b9f018671fb2bb6c3e4.avif?t=1770324837\" width=1000 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new cards, relics, chips, and characters as you play. Each run opens new strategic possibilities and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/67ca0324b6fbef91d040ace947c61641.poster.avif?t=1770324837\" width=784 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/67ca0324b6fbef91d040ace947c61641.webm?t=1770324837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312170/extras/67ca0324b6fbef91d040ace947c61641.mp4?t=1770324837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
